description.simpleText: Free Fire is a battle royale game developed and published by Garena for Android and iOS. It became the most downloaded mobile game globally in 2019. As of 2023, Free Fire had surpassed 187 million daily active users. Free Fire Max, a graphically enhanced version of Free Fire, was released globally on 28 September 2021.
